# Mobile & Responsive Design

## Touch Event Handling
```typescript
// Prevent default touch behaviors on canvas
app.view.style.touchAction = 'none';

// Use pointer events for unified mouse/touch handling
sprite.on('pointerdown', onInteraction);
sprite.on('pointermove', onDrag);
sprite.on('pointerup', onRelease);
```

## DOM-Canvas Interaction
When UI overlays PixiJS canvas:
```css
/* Main UI container should allow events to pass through */
.ui-container {
    pointer-events: none;
}

/* Only interactive elements should capture events */
.ui-button {
    pointer-events: auto;
}
```

## Responsive Sizing
```typescript
// Use proper resolution for device pixel ratio
await app.init({
    resolution: window.devicePixelRatio || 1,
    autoDensity: true
});

// Implement resize handling
app.renderer.resize(window.innerWidth, window.innerHeight);
```

